msItem.note:
Ten hymns excerpted from John of Limoges, De passione Christi. The first eight are addressed to the
                  Crucifix, Cross, Head and Five Wounds of Christ, the last two to the Virgin and St John the Evangelist: RH 14081; 20594; 23377;
                  33260; 'Ave tu sinistra' (not in RH); 39355; 'Salve vulnus dextri pedis'; 'Levi pedis perforati' (not in RH), 30648; 28714.
